review: My mother was wearing a denture since long. Denture started to become lose. Dr motivated us for dental implant and we went with the procedure. The results were excellent and after nearly 25 years my mother is having her food without the news of dentures. Thanks for the wonderful suggestions and treatment results

I have been visiting Dr Vineet for root canal treatment. While looking for dentists in Mayur I came across his clinic online. I gave him a call and requested him to come early to his clinic because I was in severe pain. Dr Kanul came 45 minutes early to see me. I am very touched by his this gesture. Highly recommended

I am glad I finally found a genuine and good dentist in Mayur Vihar phase 2. Dr. Kanul is an extremely seasoned dentist with immense experience. She does know how to take care of her patients. I can easily recommend her to everyone who is seeking dental treatment.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,
review:
I am a haemotophobic person and for me to undergo an implant procedure was a complete nightmare. Dr. Kanul was able to calm my apprehension down and explained me the complete procedure. Dr. Vineet did a splendid job with dental implants which was completely painless and quick. It’s been a week now and I am moved by the caring nature of doctors when they themselves called me up
to check my status. Highly recommended.

Very Bad experience. In my case after RCT capping was done which came out twice in a year, and every time I had to pay fee for cementing it again. But this was ok till I called for cementing again as it again came out then I was asked to pay consultation fee as well as cementing fee. * ***** **** *** * *** ***** *** ************ *** ** * ** ******* ****** *** ********* ** *** **** * **** ** **** **** **** ***** ******* **** ********* **** ** ***** *** ***** * ** ********
reply_text: As per our records your last visit was not in a span of less than 1 year. And while this pandemic time of Covid19, we are taking proper necessary precautions to minimize the chances of spread of infection therby making it a mandatory consultation fee after a period of one month. And it's a mandate to pay a consultation fee for doctors time while your visit like everywhere else. Thankyou

review: I had spaced teeth which were really uncomfortable to smile. I visited cures n care dental clinic and met Dr. kanul, she’s a wonderful dentist and takes time to explain the treatment to me. We finally agreed to start with Aligners. The clinic is small but really hi-tech. The impression was taken digitally and they even showed me post treatment results before hand. The quality of treatment is at par comparing to many fancy clinics around which charge exorbitant price. If you’re looking for treatment which is economical and yet good than you must see them.
